hey all, does anyone know why escaping using `{% raw %}` functionality is not actually working in inside a macro?

very simple example:
```{% macro my_macro() %}
  &lt;div&gt;
       {% raw %} {{"SAMPLE TEXT"}} {% endraw %}
  &lt;/div&gt;
{% endmacro %}

{{ my_macro() }}```
expected output:
```  &lt;div&gt;
       {{"SAMPLE TEXT"}}
  &lt;/div&gt;```
actual output:
```  &lt;div&gt;
       SAMPLE TEXT
  &lt;/div&gt;```
anyone know if this is a HS/HUBL bug? or am i doing something wrong?
